""SELECT `c`.`id`, `c`.`name`, `t0`.`id`, `t0`.`cycle_id`, `t0`.`year`, `t0`.`course_id`, `t0`.`subject_id`, `t0`.`id0`, `t0`.`name`, `t0`.`teacher_id`

""SELECT `c`.`id`, `c`.`name`, `t0`.`id`, `t0`.`cycle_id`, `t0`.`year`, `t0`.`course_id`, `t0`.`subject_id`, `t0`.`id0`, `t0`.`name`, `t0`.`teacher_id`

FROM `cycle` AS `c`
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT `c0`.`id`, `c0`.`cycle_id`, `c0`.`year`, `t`.`course_id`, `t`.`subject_id`, `t`.`id` AS `id0`, `t`.`name`, `t`.`teacher_id`
